        <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <label>
                        In the 2019 proposal you were asked to describe the formal processes you have in place relating to the following: <br />
                        a) Defining scope and engagement conditions with clients.<br />
                        b) Assessment of new clients and new engagement conditions including identification and management of any conflict of interest.<br />
                        c) Do you use the limitation of liability clause in your engagement contracts<br />
                        d) Briefing staff and engaging sub consultants.<br />
                        e) Internal reviewing and checking drawings, specifications, reports and other professional documents or services to be provided.<br />
                        f) Managing construction and supply contracts on behalf of clients.<br />
                        g) The identification and notification of facts that may lead to a professional liability claim.
                        h) Other risk management and quality control procedures.<br /><br />
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-9">
                    <label for="proceduremanageddetails" class="label required">
                        If such procedures are not in place, or if your procedures have changed in the past 12 months, please advise how these procedures are managed.
                        If you have not completed this proposal previously, please describe your formal processes
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="col-3">
                    @Html.TextAreaFor(m => m.PIViewModel.ProcedureManagedDetails, new { @class = "form-control", @id = "proceduremanageddetails", @type = "text", onchange = "OnChange(this.id, this.name)" })
                </div>
